title: Hey i'm new to YouTube and would like to get your guys feedback and what u guys think of my videos:)

embed.description: Just some PBE Fizz by a Fizz main :) If you guys enjoyed the video make sure to drop a like and subscribe! :D Music: JJD - Adventure [NCS Release] https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=f2xGxd9xPYA JJD * https://soundcloud.com/jjdofficial * https://www.facebook.com/jjdofficial * https://www.youtube.com/user/JJDofficial

body:
As the title says, i realise im getting quite a lot of views pretty quickly when uploading videos but not getting much feedback/subs/likes so i would like to get peoples opinions on them and what i can improve on! :D

https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=R3Ke4rAp1So  -- Heres the other video i uploaded which blew up overnight with a ton of views!

Thanks in advance and ill make sure to check back here to check for any replies :)
